		{
			description: ["Cresting the waves like a shadow of the past, this cursed vessel is crewed by skeletons that seem impossible to keep down. Every deck hides danger, every hold whispers of lost treasure and every strike you land may be fleeting. Only the bold (or the foolhardy) dare to face its relentless undead crew."]
