		{
			description: ["A sprawling underground stronghold, the Scorched Mines radiate in four cardinal directions from a central dome. Heat and shadows fill the tunnels, and danger lurks at every turn. Brave adventurers who navigate its branching paths may uncover riches, but only if they survive the hazards within."]
