			description: ["Deep within this subterranean city, the heat of molten lava and the hum of industry dominate the air. The Nether’s influence is strong here, fueling forges and animating Forge Sentinels that patrol every corridor. Only those prepared for fire and steel will survive, and claim the treasures forged within."]
