			description: ["Half-submerged in the oceans lie the petrified remains of a colossal beast, its skeletal form stretching farther than the eye can follow. Was it a creature of the deep, dragged ashore in ages past—or did it fall from the heavens themselves? No records remain, only questions carved into stone."]
